<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal" tal:omit-tag="textual">
<head tal:omit-tag="textual">
    <title tal:omit-tag="textual">Please confirm the update of your email address on <span tal:replace="domain_name">Domain name</span></title>
</head>
<body tal:omit-tag="textual">

    <h1 tal:omit-tag="textual">Please confirm the update of your email address on the IT platform <span tal:replace="domain_name">Domain name</span></h1>
    <p tal:omit-tag="textual">You, or a person having access to your account on the <span tal:replace="site_name">Site name</span> platform of <span tal:replace="domain_name">Domain name</span>, have requested us to change the email address that the <span tal:replace="domain_name">domain name</span> IT infrastructure uses to interact with you. The new email address that was requested to be used in the future is: <span tal:replace="new_email_address">New email address</span>.</p>
<p tal:omit-tag="textual">If you confirm that <span tal:replace="new_email_address">New email address</span> should be the email address that the <span tal:replace="domain_name">domain name</span> IT infrastructure should in the future use to interact with you, please click on the confirmation link below.</p>
    <a tal:attributes="href string:${check_new_email_view}" tal:omit-tag="textual">
        <span tal:replace="string:${check_new_email_view}"></span>
    </a>

    <p tal:omit-tag="textual">If you made an error, of if you did not make this request, simply ignore this e-mail.</p>

    <p tal:omit-tag="textual">Thank you for your interest in our activities.</p>
    
    <footer tal:omit-tag="textual">
        <p tal:omit-tag="textual">Best regards,</p>
        <p tal:omit-tag="textual">The team at <span tal:replace="domain_name">Site</span></p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
